      <hedline>
        <hl1>Buddy for Life</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Jennifer Lapiere on Dec 31 article on Providence, RI, colorful Mayor Buddy Cianci</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I really enjoyed Dan Barry's article on Buddy Cianci (Dec. 31). Just the week before it ran, I was in Rhode Island visiting my sister. On her kitchen counter was a bottle of Mayor's Own marinara sauce, complete with Cianci's face on the label. Having tried the sauce, I was curious to learn more about the mayor, and thanks to your article I did. The sauce, by the way, is delicious.</p>
        <p>Jennifer Lapierre  Somerville, Mass.</p>
      </block>
